OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,FA restaurant owner says he hopes a
OL,7,Fcouple's court appearance where they
OL,8,Fadmitted a series of "dine and dash"
OL,9,Foffences sends a message that theft
OL,10,Fwill not be tolerated.
OL,12,FBernard McDonagh, 41, and Ann
OL,13,FMcDonagh, 39, both of Sandfields, Port
OL,14,FTalbot, racked up large bills for food
OL,15,Fand drink at a number of restaurants
OL,16,Fbefore leaving without paying.
OL,18,FThey appeared before Swansea
OL,19,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, 8
OL,20,FMay, where they pleaded guilty to five
OL,21,Fjoint charges of fraud.
