OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,FCharges detailed how the pair first
OL,7,Fdishonestly obtained #267 of food and
OL,8,Fdrink for themselves and their family
OL,9,Fat the River House restaurant in
OL,10,FSwansea on August 9 last year, "having
OL,11,Fno intention of paying for it".
OL,13,FThey ordered #99.40 of food and drink
OL,14,Ffrom the Golden Fortune takeaway in
OL,15,FPort Talbot without paying on January
OL,16,F31, doing the same with #276.60 worth
OL,17,Fof meals from La Casona restaurant in
OL,18,FSkewen on February 23.
