OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,FOn March 27, the couple dishonestly
OL,7,Fobtained #196 of food and drink from
OL,8,FIsabella's in Porthcawl.
OL,10,FThey committed the same offence again
OL,11,Fon April 19, taking #329.10 of food
OL,12,Fand drink from Bella Ciao in Swansea.
OL,14,FSwansea Magistrates' Court heard the
OL,15,Ffive offences, which both defendants
OL,16,Fadmitted, totalled #1,168.10.
