OL,6,FThe case emerged after newly-opened
OL,7,FBella Ciao in Swansea reported that a
OL,8,Ffamily had left without paying a bill
OL,9,Fworth #329. Writing on Facebook, the
OL,10,Frestaurant described how a woman tried
OL,11,Fto pay with a savings account card
OL,12,Fwhich was declined twice before the
OL,13,Ffamily eventually left without paying.
