OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,FTyrone Rees, co-owner of the Italian
OL,7,Frestaurant business, told ITV Wales:
OL,8,F"They chose T-bone steaks. The family
OL,9,Fstarted putting their coats on and my
OL,10,Fwife realised that they were planning
OL,11,Fto leave, so my wife gently went over
OL,12,Fand said 'we still have the bill to be
OL,13,Fpaid for'.
