OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,F"The lady kindly said 'no trouble with
OL,7,Fthat, I'll sort the bill out'. She
OL,8,Fcame to the till and gave her card,
OL,9,Fbut my wife realised it was a savings
OL,10,Faccount card. It was declined the
OL,11,Ffirst time and second time, so the
OL,12,Flady said 'I must have picked the
OL,13,Fwrong card - I'll ask my husband to
OL,14,Fgive me another card, I'll be back in
OL,15,Fjust a few minutes."
OL,17,FThe family did not return to pay.
