OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,F"We put a message on social media
OL,7,Ffirst and said 'we're giving you a
OL,8,Fcouple of hours' time, if you come
OL,9,Fback and pay, we will not put this
OL,10,Fpublic. We gave them an option.
OL,12,F"It's not a mistake, it was planned to
OL,13,Fcome in and not pay. So if you're
OL,14,Fwilling to do that, to come into my
OL,15,Frestaurant, our property, why
OL,16,Fshouldn't I then say 'OK, I'll tell
OL,17,Fyou what, I'm going to let other
OL,18,Fpeople know what you do'.
