OL,3,CRestaurant owner hit by dine and dash
OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,F"We just put it on social media and
OL,7,Fsaid 'these are the people who have
OL,8,Fcome into our restaurant, they have
OL,9,Fnot paid, be aware of these people
OL,10,Fbecause they're going to do it on a
OL,11,Fregular basis.
OL,13,F"We couldn't believe how much support
OL,14,Fwe had from the local community of
OL,15,FSwansea."
OL,17,FAs for the #329 sum, Tyrone said:
OL,18,F"It's a big amount of money.
