OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,F"You can't just walk into a
OL,7,Frestaurant, eat what you want and then
OL,8,Fall of a sudden say 'let's go - I'm
OL,9,Fnot paying for this', It's wrong. It's
OL,10,Fstealing.
OL,12,F"I can't say I'm glad but hopefully
OL,13,Fthey understand they can't do this."
