OL,6,FA spokesperson for River House in
OL,7,FSwansea, which the couple defrauded
OL,8,Fout of #267 of food and drink, said
OL,9,Fafter the court hearing: "We are
OL,10,Fdelighted to hear that justice has, at
OL,11,Flast, caught up with the pair. We are
OL,12,Fgrateful to the public who have not
OL,13,Fonly been a huge help in tracking down
OL,14,Fthese criminals, but also for their
OL,15,Fhuge amount of support and messages of
OL,16,Fsupport."
