OL,4,Ccouple says stealing won't be tolerated
OL,6,FAnn McDonagh also pleaded guilty to
OL,7,Ffour counts of shoplifting, totalling
OL,8,F#1,017.60, relating to thefts at Tesco
OL,9,Fin Swansea, as well as Tommy Hilfiger
OL,10,Fand Sainsbury's at Bridgend Designer
OL,11,FOutlet. The thefts took place between
OL,12,FSeptember 6 last year and February 25
OL,13,Fthis year.
OL,15,FShe admitted one charge of wilfully
OL,16,Fobstructing a police officer in his
OL,17,Fduty at Queen's Road police station in
OL,18,FBridgend on March 13.
