OL,6,FDistrict Judge Chris James sent the
OL,7,Fcase to Swansea Crown Court for
OL,8,Fsentence.
OL,10,FHe told the defendants: "Both of you
OL,11,Fwill attend for your sentence at
OL,12,FSwansea Crown Court on May 29. Until
OL,13,Fthen, you are granted bail. It is not
OL,14,Fsubject to conditions but you must
OL,15,Fattend Swansea Crown Court at 10am on
OL,16,FMay 29. If you fail to do so, you
OL,17,Fcommit a further offence. I will, in
OL,18,Fboth of your cases, direct a pre-
OL,19,Fsentence report given the issues that
OL,20,Fhave been raised."
